@startuml C1_Manage_Vessel_Types_Process_View
title C1 – Manage Vessel Types (Process View)

actor "Port Authority Officer" as Officer
participant "VesselTypesController\n(API Layer)" as Controller
participant "VesselTypeMapper\n(Data Mapper)" as Mapper
participant "PortContext\n(EF Core)" as Context
database "Database\n(SQL / InMemory)" as DB


Officer -> Controller : POST /api/VesselTypes\n(CreateVesselTypeDTO)
Controller -> Mapper : Converte DTO → Entidade de Domínio
Mapper --> Controller : Retorna objeto VesselType

Controller -> Context : Adiciona entidade VesselType
Context -> DB : Persiste dados (SaveChanges)
DB --> Context : Confirma inserção
Context --> Controller : OK

Controller --> Officer : HTTP 201 Created\n(VesselTypeDTO)


@enduml
